{"tid":1710392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"講真我真係對大家好失望。又一間要入大裝修名單","createTime":"2019-11-12T07:23:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T19:47:50.000Z","uid":288018,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0b44aed7623bd12aa476e45b42d96446a1cb385f","tid":1710392,"uid":288018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T07:23:02.000Z","msg":"話說我係尖沙咀附近返工，有日同事啲去左<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">厚福街</span></span>入面呢間鋪頭<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">2DP</span></strong></span>食飯。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聽到佢地既員工係到講，（<ins><span style=\"color: gold;\">班防暴都係自我保護先開槍姐 ，前面啲曱甴唔走 。用催淚彈驅散佢地都好正常。我覺得好合理Wo。仲有啊，啲曱甴次次都著到條褲咁短 又吊帶 。好明顯係想色誘呀sir姐。比呀sir捉返警署強姦抽水都係自己囉黎</span></ins>）<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌你老母 你班仆街係咪無人性架 良心都無撚埋，<br />\n跟住佢地幾個講仲要大大聲驚死無人知,佢地仲要係open Kitchen。<br />\n心諗你地識唔識咩叫尊重立場嫁，仲要係到笑。人命黎嫁屌佢老母無家教。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"color: gold;\">突然有位廚房後生仔話未食過tg wo話好想試下係咩味。之後又有一個後生女話點解落親街都要食tg，好心啲曱甴死開啲啦，阻住我食飯行街。<br />\n</span></ins><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以我所識嘅素食餐廳員工都好有愛心，原來可以有啲咁噁心嘅人。<br />\n我食完今次之後我無撚再去過，我返到公司都叫左其他同事唔好幫襯呢間<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>2DP</strong></span></span>。而且餐廳廁所有真曱甴囉，好噁心。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">發生左咁多事，大家都仲去光顧啲無良心食肆既話。你地過唔過意得去 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n比錢佢地賺。仲要聽佢地點樣屌鳩啲示威者，你地個良心去左邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A8fikg0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA8fikg0.png&h=d1d1b5c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"55c32a4b8fa86defd3d757ace7e3ab5b8ec2d50c","tid":1710392,"uid":336561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T07:56:39.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fec3d741cb74047ed9a6626e3da7217b8717d99","tid":1710392,"uid":288018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55c32a4b8fa86defd3d757ace7e3ab5b8ec2d50c","tid":1710392,"uid":336561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T07:56:39.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T07:57:57.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"51228ffcc49b3cf21d113f236b1861fb8c040106","tid":1710392,"uid":288018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T19:47:50.000Z","msg":"自推"}]}